1
00:00:22,464 --> 00:00:26,432
♪Should we forget yesterday's sorrows♪

2
00:00:26,432 --> 00:00:29,728
♪And the dazed confusion♪

3
00:00:30,976 --> 00:00:33,681
♪Should we let go of♪

4
00:00:33,681 --> 00:00:35,904
♪The stubborn madness♪

5
00:00:35,904 --> 00:00:39,072
♪And naive recklessness now♪

6
00:00:40,192 --> 00:00:43,840
♪Those years, those faces♪

7
00:00:44,992 --> 00:00:48,763
♪Those old scars we can't erase♪

8
00:00:49,824 --> 00:00:52,460
♪Tears streaming, facing the light♪

9
00:00:53,152 --> 00:00:57,594
♪Piercing the sorrow within♪

10
00:01:08,716 --> 00:01:12,736
♪The road ahead's long,
stumbling all the way♪

11
00:01:13,536 --> 00:01:18,076
♪The wounds we've borne
are medals hidden within♪

12
00:01:18,336 --> 00:01:22,391
♪Standing alone on an open plain♪

13
00:01:23,168 --> 00:01:26,851
♪We gaze at the stars♪

14
00:01:31,228 --> 00:01:34,816
=The Dream Maker=

15
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:37,971
=Episode 17=

16
00:01:40,754 --> 00:01:43,634
(Dongjiang Provincial Government)

17
00:01:46,546 --> 00:01:47,106
Mr. Zheng.

18
00:01:48,626 --> 00:01:49,425
Li, you're here.

19
00:01:49,785 --> 00:01:50,285
Sit.

20
00:01:51,186 --> 00:01:51,785
Are you tired?

21
00:01:53,266 --> 00:01:53,865
Have water.

22
00:01:54,746 --> 00:01:55,345
Thank you.

23
00:01:55,865 --> 00:01:56,666
I've registered.

24
00:01:57,225 --> 00:01:57,826
Wait here.

25
00:01:58,225 --> 00:01:59,585
Mr. Zhang is in a meeting inside.

26
00:02:01,585 --> 00:02:02,505
What kind of meeting?

27
00:02:04,585 --> 00:02:06,505
Seems to be about economic affairs.

28
00:02:10,625 --> 00:02:11,346
Don't be nervous.

29
00:02:12,106 --> 00:02:12,865
I'm not nervous.

30
00:02:18,106 --> 00:02:19,425
Mr. Zheng, don't be nervous.

31
00:02:19,506 --> 00:02:20,185
I'm not nervous.

32
00:02:20,625 --> 00:02:21,705
Your leg is shaking.

33
00:02:22,705 --> 00:02:24,386
My leg isn't shaking. Is it?

34
00:02:26,666 --> 00:02:28,986
It's not about nerves, just a habit.

35
00:02:30,145 --> 00:02:31,986
I've met more than one senior official.

36
00:02:32,585 --> 00:02:36,166
I wasn't even afraid of speaking
in front of thousands of cadres.

37
00:02:36,346 --> 00:02:37,425
Is it the same?

38
00:02:38,946 --> 00:02:39,705
Not really.

39
00:02:41,506 --> 00:02:42,006
True.

40
00:02:42,666 --> 00:02:45,240
Tens of thousands
of Yuehai residents are counting on me.

41
00:02:45,816 --> 00:02:48,145
I'm not nervous. I can't be nervous.

42
00:02:48,585 --> 00:02:49,585
I'm not nervous at all.

43
00:02:51,025 --> 00:02:51,905
I can't be nervous.

44
00:02:53,425 --> 00:02:54,386
Then stop shaking.

45
00:02:55,386 --> 00:02:56,585
I'm not shaking.

46
00:03:04,106 --> 00:03:05,865
Are you from Yuehai?

47
00:03:06,826 --> 00:03:07,326
Yes.

48
00:03:07,705 --> 00:03:09,585
I'm Mr. Zhang's secretary.

49
00:03:09,986 --> 00:03:11,025
He is still in session.

50
00:03:11,266 --> 00:03:13,066
He likely won't be available
for a while.

51
00:03:13,346 --> 00:03:15,745
When will the meeting end?

52
00:03:17,946 --> 00:03:18,745
Probably

53
00:03:18,925 --> 00:03:20,346
around 1 PM or 2 PM.

54
00:03:20,745 --> 00:03:22,506
Then that's too late.

55
00:03:22,546 --> 00:03:23,786
The papers are already printed.

56
00:03:25,266 --> 00:03:27,025
Sir, I remember

57
00:03:27,546 --> 00:03:30,185
that economic planning meetings,
before finalizing decisions,

58
00:03:30,386 --> 00:03:32,226
usually reserve half an hour

59
00:03:32,226 --> 00:03:34,305
for discussion and breaks, right?

60
00:03:37,946 --> 00:03:39,226
She previously

61
00:03:39,305 --> 00:03:40,986
served as a secretary too.

62
00:03:41,546 --> 00:03:43,226
Could you relay messages to Mr. Zhang?

63
00:03:43,465 --> 00:03:45,786
We just need ten minutes of his time.

64
00:03:45,986 --> 00:03:46,486
Right.

65
00:03:46,546 --> 00:03:47,625
Just ten minutes.

66
00:03:51,425 --> 00:03:53,025
Here's the Pingchuan County Annals.

67
00:03:53,425 --> 00:03:55,226
(Pingchuan County Annals)
Please give it to Mr. Zhang.

68
00:03:55,585 --> 00:03:57,585
It's a small gift for him.

69
00:04:04,178 --> 00:04:05,304
(Part Five: Culture
Chapter 28: Education)

70
00:04:16,546 --> 00:04:17,046
Alright.

71
00:04:17,346 --> 00:04:18,786
I'll only deliver your message.

72
00:04:19,346 --> 00:04:20,425
No guarantees.

73
00:04:20,745 --> 00:04:21,346
Okay.

74
00:04:21,606 --> 00:04:22,106
Very well.

75
00:04:22,106 --> 00:04:22,786
Wait here.

76
00:04:22,825 --> 00:04:23,325
Okay.

77
00:04:23,425 --> 00:04:24,146
Thank you.

78
00:04:24,146 --> 00:04:25,265
- No problem.
- Thank you.

79
00:04:25,385 --> 00:04:25,885
No problem.

80
00:04:27,945 --> 00:04:29,546
What's hidden in the annals?

81
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:56,914
(Yuehai Column: Seven-up, Eight-down
No Land Sales. What's Next for Yuehai?)

82
00:05:00,786 --> 00:05:04,120
(Dongjiang Provincial Government)

83
00:05:30,906 --> 00:05:31,786
Hello?

84
00:05:32,625 --> 00:05:33,625
Are you still here?

85
00:05:33,945 --> 00:05:34,445
Yes.

86
00:05:45,426 --> 00:05:48,600
(Part Five: Culture
Chapter 28: Education)

87
00:05:50,425 --> 00:05:51,106
Li.

88
00:05:51,546 --> 00:05:54,185
(Pingchuan County Annals)
You compiled the annals?

89
00:05:55,586 --> 00:05:56,106
Yes.

90
00:05:57,586 --> 00:05:58,625
After all these years,

91
00:05:58,786 --> 00:06:00,546
you have
found so much historical material

92
00:06:01,146 --> 00:06:02,185
and compiled it.

93
00:06:02,865 --> 00:06:05,546
It even
includes my ballad-collecting work.

94
00:06:07,586 --> 00:06:08,466
I'd nearly forgotten.

95
00:06:09,505 --> 00:06:11,625
Mr. Zhang, it's my duty.

96
00:06:13,026 --> 00:06:14,346
I was so young then.

97
00:06:14,786 --> 00:06:16,265
Still in high school.

98
00:06:17,466 --> 00:06:19,352
I just thought we needed

99
00:06:19,864 --> 00:06:22,185
to compile our cultural heritage.

100
00:06:23,346 --> 00:06:25,906
I appreciate this thoughtful gift.

101
00:06:26,346 --> 00:06:27,106
I'll keep it.

102
00:06:30,385 --> 00:06:31,825
You've traveled so far

103
00:06:32,346 --> 00:06:33,625
and put in such effort.

104
00:06:34,546 --> 00:06:35,906
You even convinced my secretary.

105
00:06:36,466 --> 00:06:38,466
Just come straight to the point.

106
00:06:39,625 --> 00:06:40,226
Mr. Zhang,

107
00:06:40,745 --> 00:06:41,586
this matter

108
00:06:41,906 --> 00:06:44,385
isn't trivial yet significant,

109
00:06:44,945 --> 00:06:47,185
requiring provincial-level mediation.

110
00:06:47,466 --> 00:06:49,706
We've notified county leadership

111
00:06:50,026 --> 00:06:50,986
before approaching you.

112
00:07:11,586 --> 00:07:13,505
Decheng, Qiuping.

113
00:07:15,106 --> 00:07:17,026
You've come fully prepared.

114
00:07:17,906 --> 00:07:18,406
Yes.

115
00:07:18,786 --> 00:07:21,466
The "seven-up, eight-down" issue
with the city construction fee

116
00:07:21,505 --> 00:07:23,625
was debated under my direction.

117
00:07:24,666 --> 00:07:25,226
However,

118
00:07:26,505 --> 00:07:27,865
you can't expect me to help you

119
00:07:28,385 --> 00:07:29,786
every time something goes wrong.

120
00:07:30,745 --> 00:07:33,546
What you're doing
in Yuehai is meant to spark debate.

121
00:07:34,586 --> 00:07:35,945
If you can't even handle it,

122
00:07:36,825 --> 00:07:37,786
just give up.

123
00:07:38,825 --> 00:07:40,385
Mr. Zhang, here's the thing.

124
00:07:40,906 --> 00:07:43,065
Personally, I'm not afraid.

125
00:07:43,666 --> 00:07:45,986
Taking responsibility?
I can handle that.

126
00:07:46,505 --> 00:07:49,065
I can accept
either demotion or punishment.

127
00:07:49,865 --> 00:07:51,986
But Yuehai is still too fragile.

128
00:07:52,625 --> 00:07:54,745
It's not ready
to face storms like this yet.

129
00:07:55,505 --> 00:07:56,586
It's like an infant.

130
00:07:57,026 --> 00:07:59,065
It can't fight like an adult.

131
00:07:59,305 --> 00:08:01,226
But secrets never stay buried forever.

132
00:08:03,625 --> 00:08:05,305
Yuehai's experiments and experiences

133
00:08:05,786 --> 00:08:07,865
will eventually become known outside.

134
00:08:08,505 --> 00:08:09,906
Today, it's "New City Life".

135
00:08:11,185 --> 00:08:13,505
What if another newspaper comes
tomorrow?

136
00:08:14,666 --> 00:08:15,346
What will you do?

137
00:08:16,906 --> 00:08:17,656
Come to me again?

138
00:08:18,146 --> 00:08:21,185
Mr. Zhang, we understand your point.

139
00:08:22,106 --> 00:08:23,466
So, Mr. Zheng means

140
00:08:23,825 --> 00:08:26,265
he just hopes for more time.

141
00:08:26,706 --> 00:08:28,666
Wait until Yuehai truly grows up

142
00:08:28,986 --> 00:08:30,586
and can withstand any storms.

143
00:08:31,346 --> 00:08:32,865
Then, we'll welcome all coverage.

144
00:08:33,826 --> 00:08:36,466
I understand your concerns.

145
00:08:38,665 --> 00:08:39,986
But I must criticize you.

146
00:08:40,466 --> 00:08:43,186
The whole country
is exploring uncharted waters.

147
00:08:45,466 --> 00:08:46,986
Have faith in the people.

148
00:08:48,025 --> 00:08:50,625
Have faith in our future.

149
00:08:53,745 --> 00:08:54,245
Six months.

150
00:08:57,706 --> 00:08:59,665
Mr. Zhang, what do you mean?

151
00:08:59,865 --> 00:09:01,625
Though your methods were flawed,

152
00:09:02,466 --> 00:09:04,625
your intention was for Yuehai's people.

153
00:09:06,106 --> 00:09:07,346
That moves me deeply.

154
00:09:08,346 --> 00:09:09,745
I'll talk with relevant parties.

155
00:09:10,826 --> 00:09:12,265
I'll try to buy you six months.

156
00:09:13,226 --> 00:09:13,944
After six months,

157
00:09:14,226 --> 00:09:16,586
whether "New City Life"
or other publications,

158
00:09:17,025 --> 00:09:19,426
when they research and report on Yuehai,

159
00:09:19,745 --> 00:09:20,306
Yuehai

160
00:09:21,466 --> 00:09:22,346
must cooperate fully,

161
00:09:22,946 --> 00:09:23,665
open its door,

162
00:09:24,505 --> 00:09:26,066
and let people judge.

163
00:09:27,226 --> 00:09:29,265
But I can only try, no guarantees.

164
00:09:30,265 --> 00:09:32,426
The final decision rests
with the authorities.

165
00:09:32,865 --> 00:09:33,785
Is that clear?

166
00:09:34,665 --> 00:09:35,426
Sure.

167
00:09:47,785 --> 00:09:49,625
Stop! Stop the presses!

168
00:09:49,986 --> 00:09:52,025
Halt them! Stop right now!

169
00:09:52,306 --> 00:09:53,145
Shut it all down.

170
00:09:56,466 --> 00:09:58,905
Six months? Editor Xiao,
how is that possible?

171
00:09:59,346 --> 00:10:01,066
In six months, similar cases nationwide

172
00:10:01,106 --> 00:10:02,545
will keep emerging endlessly!

173
00:10:02,566 --> 00:10:03,992
By then, my Yuehai features

174
00:10:03,992 --> 00:10:05,745
will completely lose attention!

175
00:10:05,826 --> 00:10:07,145
I know that.

176
00:10:07,426 --> 00:10:10,665
But the decision is final.
It can't be changed.

177
00:10:12,545 --> 00:10:14,785
Editor Xiao, I still
don't understand why!

178
00:10:14,986 --> 00:10:16,826
Didn't you personally
approve my articles?

179
00:10:16,826 --> 00:10:18,745
You told me to write some great pieces.

180
00:10:18,785 --> 00:10:19,745
I wrote it.

181
00:10:19,905 --> 00:10:20,586
But in the end...

182
00:10:20,665 --> 00:10:21,586
Du,

183
00:10:22,106 --> 00:10:23,865
when I got the call, I felt the same.

184
00:10:24,186 --> 00:10:25,586
I couldn't accept it either.

185
00:10:26,066 --> 00:10:27,186
But this is life.

186
00:10:27,826 --> 00:10:30,265
You have to face setback after setback,

187
00:10:30,306 --> 00:10:32,066
forcing you to face reality.

188
00:10:33,385 --> 00:10:34,066
But I trust you.

189
00:10:34,625 --> 00:10:36,785
Since you wrote two great articles,

190
00:10:36,946 --> 00:10:40,346
you can write 20
and even 200 better ones!

191
00:10:43,106 --> 00:10:45,066
Editor Xiao, this isn't about trust.

192
00:10:45,426 --> 00:10:46,226
I can't take it.

193
00:10:46,226 --> 00:10:48,145
At least give me a reason!

194
00:10:48,545 --> 00:10:50,505
All I can say is
Zheng Decheng is formidable.

195
00:10:50,745 --> 00:10:53,304
He went straight to Mr. Zhang
of the Provincial Committee.

196
00:10:53,826 --> 00:10:55,466
Mr. Zhang personally gave the order.

197
00:10:59,586 --> 00:11:00,865
He knows Mr. Zhang?

198
00:11:02,306 --> 00:11:04,986
Guess who went
with Zheng Decheng to see Mr. Zhang?

199
00:11:06,545 --> 00:11:07,045
Who?

200
00:11:07,385 --> 00:11:10,905
Yuehai's Town Mayor,
your girlfriend, Li Qiuping.

201
00:11:16,346 --> 00:11:16,946
Du Tao.

202
00:11:17,785 --> 00:11:18,625
- Ms. Li.
- Du Tao.

203
00:11:19,745 --> 00:11:20,306
Ms. Li.

204
00:11:21,706 --> 00:11:23,145
Didn't Mr. Du go back?

205
00:11:23,346 --> 00:11:24,865
His colleagues said he came to Yuehai.

206
00:11:25,905 --> 00:11:26,665
He's in Yuehai?

207
00:11:27,745 --> 00:11:28,426
Haven't seen him.

208
00:11:32,025 --> 00:11:32,625
He's here?

209
00:11:48,498 --> 00:11:52,370
(Yuehai Column: Seven-up, Eight-down
No Land Sales. What's Next for Yuehai?)

210
00:12:08,306 --> 00:12:09,186
Do you have any idea

211
00:12:10,066 --> 00:12:12,545
how hard it is
to get a new article published?

212
00:12:14,665 --> 00:12:16,385
I watched it roll through the press.

213
00:12:17,226 --> 00:12:18,186
It was already printed.

214
00:12:21,745 --> 00:12:22,346
Sorry.

215
00:12:24,625 --> 00:12:27,186
I truly can't
let your articles get published.

216
00:12:28,586 --> 00:12:29,586
But trust me.

217
00:12:30,665 --> 00:12:31,426
Wait six months.

218
00:12:32,306 --> 00:12:34,306
- After six months, Yuehai...
- Six months?

219
00:12:35,106 --> 00:12:36,665
Will it still be news after six months?

220
00:12:38,545 --> 00:12:40,306
It's pointless to talk about this now.

221
00:12:40,986 --> 00:12:42,625
All because of your concerns,

222
00:12:42,865 --> 00:12:44,265
the Yuehai Column is gone.

223
00:12:45,306 --> 00:12:45,865
It's gone.

224
00:12:47,265 --> 00:12:48,346
Is my career

225
00:12:48,346 --> 00:12:50,346
so insignificant in your eyes?

226
00:12:54,066 --> 00:12:54,665
Du Tao.

227
00:12:58,186 --> 00:12:58,946
I'm sorry.

228
00:13:00,346 --> 00:13:02,905
But this concerns the entire fate
of Yuehai.

229
00:13:02,986 --> 00:13:04,025
The fate of Yuehai?

230
00:13:04,545 --> 00:13:05,745
Then, what about my fate?

231
00:13:15,385 --> 00:13:16,706
Guess how I felt on the way here?

232
00:13:18,586 --> 00:13:19,706
I was completely dazed.

233
00:13:20,586 --> 00:13:22,706
When I snapped out of it,
I was already in Yuehai.

234
00:13:23,226 --> 00:13:24,346
That's when I realized

235
00:13:24,946 --> 00:13:25,665
all these years,

236
00:13:26,145 --> 00:13:28,120
I'd driven 300 kilometers
to Pingchuan many times.

237
00:13:28,665 --> 00:13:30,745
It's like I've been driving by instinct.

238
00:13:39,625 --> 00:13:41,106
We've been together for ten years.

239
00:13:43,385 --> 00:13:45,545
I've been trying
to cut the long distance between us.

240
00:13:46,186 --> 00:13:47,946
But why are there
always so many obstacles?

241
00:13:49,346 --> 00:13:53,025
After graduation, you couldn't stay
in the provincial capital for your mom.

242
00:13:53,346 --> 00:13:53,986
I understood.

243
00:13:55,025 --> 00:13:56,905
Later, when your family
improved somewhat,

244
00:13:56,905 --> 00:13:58,306
my mom finally got you a job

245
00:13:58,306 --> 00:14:00,385
at the Grain Bureau,
but you didn't want it.

246
00:14:00,946 --> 00:14:01,706
I understood too.

247
00:14:02,826 --> 00:14:03,986
Now, you've come to Yuehai.

248
00:14:04,265 --> 00:14:05,785
Yuehai has your ambitions.

249
00:14:05,865 --> 00:14:06,785
I can understand.

250
00:14:06,905 --> 00:14:08,466
But what about my ambitions?

251
00:14:09,625 --> 00:14:12,265
Do you have any idea how much I've put
into the Yuehai Column?

252
00:14:13,306 --> 00:14:15,106
I finally got this opportunity.

253
00:14:15,785 --> 00:14:16,545
Finally.

254
00:14:16,986 --> 00:14:19,265
Why can't you understand me,
just this once?

255
00:14:27,466 --> 00:14:27,966
Yes,

256
00:14:29,145 --> 00:14:29,745
I admit

257
00:14:30,586 --> 00:14:31,865
I do have my own motives.

258
00:14:33,385 --> 00:14:34,625
It's because you're too good.

259
00:14:36,545 --> 00:14:38,385
You've always shone so brightly.

260
00:14:39,466 --> 00:14:40,865
I pushed myself so hard

261
00:14:41,665 --> 00:14:43,706
just to stand
shoulder to shoulder with you.

262
00:14:44,265 --> 00:14:45,466
And what did you do?

263
00:14:46,226 --> 00:14:47,505
You destroyed my chance.

264
00:14:51,665 --> 00:14:52,385
Li Qiuping,

265
00:14:53,785 --> 00:14:55,186
how much more do I have to give up?

266
00:14:55,306 --> 00:14:57,306
Do you know
how tiring it is being your boyfriend?

267
00:14:59,865 --> 00:15:00,545
Du Tao.

268
00:15:01,426 --> 00:15:03,545
You've been so nice to me.

269
00:15:04,265 --> 00:15:06,745
Your tolerance,
understanding, and support,

270
00:15:06,946 --> 00:15:08,706
I keep all that in mind.

271
00:15:09,025 --> 00:15:10,106
I also want

272
00:15:10,106 --> 00:15:13,106
to help and support you
when you're in need.

273
00:15:15,346 --> 00:15:16,385
But this time,

274
00:15:17,265 --> 00:15:18,706
I have to make this choice.

275
00:15:19,346 --> 00:15:22,385
I don't dare hope
you'll understand me again.

276
00:15:23,706 --> 00:15:24,946
Please don't doubt your place

277
00:15:24,946 --> 00:15:28,186
and importance in my heart, okay?

278
00:15:36,365 --> 00:15:38,265
I have over 300 kilometers to drive.

279
00:15:39,346 --> 00:15:39,986
I'm tired.

280
00:15:40,050 --> 00:15:42,295
♪You came quietly♪

281
00:15:44,205 --> 00:15:46,861
♪And left quietly♪

282
00:15:48,888 --> 00:15:50,776
♪Perhaps one day♪

283
00:15:51,090 --> 00:15:53,078
♪It won't really matter♪

284
00:15:53,500 --> 00:15:55,670
♪Who will still remember♪

285
00:15:57,127 --> 00:15:59,632
♪You and me♪

286
00:16:02,098 --> 00:16:03,960
♪You are a beam of light♪

287
00:16:04,216 --> 00:16:06,424
♪In dazzling years♪

288
00:16:06,674 --> 00:16:10,047
♪Shining on me alone in the dark♪

289
00:16:11,026 --> 00:16:13,016
♪You are a boat♪

290
00:16:13,016 --> 00:16:15,320
♪Carrying our dreams♪

291
00:16:15,538 --> 00:16:19,416
♪Braving the wind and waves
towards the light♪

292
00:16:21,997 --> 00:16:23,928
♪Some are happy♪

293
00:16:23,928 --> 00:16:25,988
♪Leaning on and embracing each other♪

294
00:16:26,450 --> 00:16:30,258
♪Sharing the warmth of their love♪

295
00:16:30,520 --> 00:16:32,376
(The Female Town Mayor's Wisdom)

296
00:16:32,376 --> 00:16:34,652
(An Apology Meeting for One)

297
00:16:35,602 --> 00:16:38,483
♪Your shadow in the sunset♪

298
00:16:39,858 --> 00:16:41,592
♪Some are waiting♪

299
00:16:41,592 --> 00:16:43,853
♪For passengers in life♪

300
00:16:44,505 --> 00:16:45,005
Hey, Qiang!

301
00:16:45,946 --> 00:16:47,545
Hai, you're finally here.

302
00:16:47,545 --> 00:16:48,826
We thought you'd forgotten all

303
00:16:48,826 --> 00:16:49,785
about us.

304
00:16:49,826 --> 00:16:51,826
Don't be ridiculous! We're friends.

305
00:16:52,106 --> 00:16:53,785
Since I'm late, I'll pay for the movie.

306
00:16:53,865 --> 00:16:54,946
- Great!
- Awesome!

307
00:16:54,966 --> 00:16:55,466
Let's go.

308
00:16:55,466 --> 00:16:56,265
- Let's go.
- Yeah.

309
00:16:56,562 --> 00:16:58,002
(Cinema)

310
00:16:59,125 --> 00:16:59,625
(No Credit)
Sir.

311
00:16:59,625 --> 00:17:00,125
Welcome.

312
00:17:00,466 --> 00:17:01,066
Six people.

313
00:17:02,706 --> 00:17:03,206
Have a seat.

314
00:17:05,065 --> 00:17:06,206
I have exactly enough money.

315
00:17:10,785 --> 00:17:11,285
Look,

316
00:17:11,666 --> 00:17:13,545
it's five jiao per person now.

317
00:17:13,666 --> 00:17:15,505
Three yuan for six people.

318
00:17:15,666 --> 00:17:17,065
You're one yuan short.

319
00:17:17,226 --> 00:17:18,745
When did the price go up?

320
00:17:23,386 --> 00:17:25,505
Don't pay! I said it's my treat.

321
00:17:29,345 --> 00:17:31,025
We didn't know you raised the price.

322
00:17:31,585 --> 00:17:32,305
Put it on tab?

323
00:17:32,706 --> 00:17:34,146
We're regulars.

324
00:17:34,505 --> 00:17:35,505
He'll pay up next time.

325
00:17:35,545 --> 00:17:37,126
But look,

326
00:17:37,426 --> 00:17:38,545
