327
00:17:40,050 --> 00:17:41,785
(No Credit)

328
00:17:41,785 --> 00:17:44,466
No what?

329
00:17:45,065 --> 00:17:46,265
No Cradit.

330
00:17:47,505 --> 00:17:49,065
Sir, just this time?

331
00:17:49,426 --> 00:17:49,946
No way!

332
00:17:50,345 --> 00:17:50,845
Sir.

333
00:17:51,265 --> 00:17:51,765
Check out.

334
00:17:52,626 --> 00:17:53,386
And cigarettes.

335
00:17:53,426 --> 00:17:53,926
Here you go.

336
00:17:57,146 --> 00:17:57,666
Ten yuan.

337
00:17:58,146 --> 00:17:58,906
Isn't this Hei?

338
00:18:01,025 --> 00:18:01,825
Sure is.

339
00:18:02,065 --> 00:18:03,446
For the cigarettes and drinks.

340
00:18:04,626 --> 00:18:05,626
Want some tea eggs, guys?

341
00:18:05,785 --> 00:18:06,585
No need.

342
00:18:06,626 --> 00:18:08,466
A pack of peanuts. Come on.

343
00:18:08,585 --> 00:18:09,505
Keep the change.

344
00:18:09,626 --> 00:18:10,706
Okay. Thanks, sir.

345
00:18:11,825 --> 00:18:12,745
I want to eat eggs too.

346
00:18:14,545 --> 00:18:16,505
Hai, Qiang?

347
00:18:17,505 --> 00:18:19,946
Bao, and Zhuang!

348
00:18:20,146 --> 00:18:22,466
What's going on here?

349
00:18:23,226 --> 00:18:25,505
They're one yuan short
for the movie tickets.

350
00:18:26,866 --> 00:18:28,906
Hei, didn't you go to Guangzhou?

351
00:18:29,305 --> 00:18:30,105
Why are you back?

352
00:18:30,426 --> 00:18:32,146
My cousin is getting married.

353
00:18:32,305 --> 00:18:34,146
I came back yesterday for her wedding.

354
00:18:35,626 --> 00:18:37,626
Sir, this is my buddy.

355
00:18:38,505 --> 00:18:39,505
Come on, my treat.

356
00:18:39,505 --> 00:18:40,805
My treat.

357
00:18:40,825 --> 00:18:41,785
Go inside.

358
00:18:41,785 --> 00:18:42,505
It's on me.

359
00:18:42,505 --> 00:18:43,466
Come on in.

360
00:18:43,466 --> 00:18:44,345
This is my buddy.

361
00:18:44,426 --> 00:18:45,146
Hello.

362
00:18:48,626 --> 00:18:50,265
(Chunmei Printery)
Thanks, sir. Bye!

363
00:18:55,466 --> 00:18:56,426
Someone, come out!

364
00:18:58,305 --> 00:19:00,906
How did Hei suddenly get rich?

365
00:19:01,226 --> 00:19:03,426
He bought us movie tickets and drinks.

366
00:19:03,666 --> 00:19:05,706
How much did he earn
with his uncle in Guangzhou?

367
00:19:05,906 --> 00:19:06,745
A lot, I guess.

368
00:19:08,426 --> 00:19:09,466
Hai, how much do you earn?

369
00:19:10,305 --> 00:19:11,386
36 yuan a month.

370
00:19:12,186 --> 00:19:13,666
36 yuan?

371
00:19:14,666 --> 00:19:15,906
(Printery)
Where is everyone?

372
00:19:20,906 --> 00:19:21,745
Ms. Gao.

373
00:19:22,866 --> 00:19:23,426
Zhiqiang.

374
00:19:23,706 --> 00:19:24,226
Are you okay?

375
00:19:24,226 --> 00:19:24,785
I'm fine.

376
00:19:24,785 --> 00:19:26,545
A thorn on the box pricked my hand.

377
00:19:26,785 --> 00:19:27,626
Let us help you,

378
00:19:27,706 --> 00:19:28,206
Ms. Gao.

379
00:19:28,265 --> 00:19:29,025
No need.

380
00:19:29,305 --> 00:19:30,426
Thank you so much.

381
00:19:30,466 --> 00:19:30,966
Not at all.

382
00:19:31,065 --> 00:19:32,386
- Not at all.
- Watch for thorns!

383
00:19:32,386 --> 00:19:33,386
- One, two, three, lift!
- Careful.

384
00:19:33,745 --> 00:19:35,105
Alright. This is heavy.

385
00:19:35,345 --> 00:19:35,946
Slow down.

386
00:19:36,505 --> 00:19:37,505
To the left.

387
00:19:38,226 --> 00:19:38,745
This way.

388
00:19:39,065 --> 00:19:39,585
This way.

389
00:19:39,866 --> 00:19:40,785
- Thanks.
- Turn.

390
00:19:40,986 --> 00:19:42,146
Slow down. It's too heavy.

391
00:19:42,866 --> 00:19:43,386
Come on.

392
00:19:45,146 --> 00:19:45,825
Thanks.

393
00:19:46,446 --> 00:19:46,946
Let's go.

394
00:19:46,946 --> 00:19:47,906
Be careful, please.

395
00:19:47,946 --> 00:19:48,626
Be careful.

396
00:19:51,025 --> 00:19:51,585
Thank you.

397
00:19:52,866 --> 00:19:54,345
Thank you so much.

398
00:19:55,186 --> 00:19:56,146
Wait a second.

399
00:19:56,466 --> 00:19:57,065
Well...

400
00:19:59,626 --> 00:20:00,785
A token of appreciation.

401
00:20:03,105 --> 00:20:03,745
Well...

402
00:20:05,785 --> 00:20:06,666
Go buy some ice cream.

403
00:20:09,065 --> 00:20:09,785
Take it. Come on.

404
00:20:10,226 --> 00:20:11,226
Take it.

405
00:20:11,626 --> 00:20:13,386
I really appreciate your help.

406
00:20:13,505 --> 00:20:14,466
Thank you, Ms. Gao.

407
00:20:14,585 --> 00:20:15,986
- You're welcome. See you.
- Thanks.

408
00:20:16,386 --> 00:20:16,946
Thanks again.

409
00:20:17,146 --> 00:20:17,706
- Bye.
- Thanks.

410
00:20:18,025 --> 00:20:18,666
(Chunmei Printery)
Not at all.

411
00:20:24,305 --> 00:20:25,146
Someone, come here.

412
00:20:27,226 --> 00:20:28,825
I just did her a small favor

413
00:20:29,065 --> 00:20:30,105
and earned me

414
00:20:30,105 --> 00:20:31,745
nearly half a month's wages.

415
00:20:32,545 --> 00:20:33,505
Wow.

416
00:20:36,186 --> 00:20:37,545
Is this ice cream good?

417
00:20:37,706 --> 00:20:38,866
It's good.

418
00:20:40,986 --> 00:20:41,825
Hello, Ms. Yang.

419
00:20:43,146 --> 00:20:43,906
Ms. Li.

420
00:20:45,866 --> 00:20:46,626
Ping.

421
00:20:47,265 --> 00:20:49,466
Please thank Mr. Lin for me.

422
00:20:50,386 --> 00:20:53,706
This wheelchair is so good for me.

423
00:20:54,025 --> 00:20:54,706
Okay.

424
00:20:55,466 --> 00:20:57,146
Don't worry. I'll definitely tell him.

425
00:20:58,025 --> 00:20:58,545
Ping,

426
00:21:00,025 --> 00:21:03,906
being a Town Mayor isn't better
than having an ice cream.

427
00:21:05,946 --> 00:21:07,825
If you have nowhere
to vent your frustrations,

428
00:21:08,105 --> 00:21:09,906
just come find me.

429
00:21:10,426 --> 00:21:12,305
I won't tell anyone else.

430
00:21:15,545 --> 00:21:17,946
It's a deal then.
Please don't find me annoying.

431
00:21:18,186 --> 00:21:19,105
Of course not.

432
00:21:19,626 --> 00:21:22,666
Actually, I'm the same. I have nowhere
to vent my frustrations either.

433
00:21:24,305 --> 00:21:26,426
I'm quite old now.

434
00:21:26,825 --> 00:21:28,345
Who knows how many more times

435
00:21:28,745 --> 00:21:30,906
I can eat such delicious things?

436
00:21:32,265 --> 00:21:32,866
Ping,

437
00:21:34,386 --> 00:21:35,946
I'm nagging you like this

438
00:21:36,666 --> 00:21:39,505
because I have something to ask of you.

439
00:21:39,825 --> 00:21:40,505
Go ahead.

440
00:21:41,745 --> 00:21:44,065
Xiaohai has a hard life.

441
00:21:44,545 --> 00:21:46,025
His parents passed away early.

442
00:21:46,265 --> 00:21:47,946
I'm getting old myself.

443
00:21:48,505 --> 00:21:50,386
Who knows when I'll be gone?

444
00:21:51,305 --> 00:21:52,025
So,

445
00:21:53,946 --> 00:21:54,906
I hope

446
00:21:56,545 --> 00:21:58,825
you'll look out for him in the future.

447
00:22:00,065 --> 00:22:01,986
Don't worry. I definitely will.

448
00:22:20,626 --> 00:22:21,226
Sir.

449
00:22:22,146 --> 00:22:23,585
Do you need help?

450
00:22:23,745 --> 00:22:24,866
No, thanks.

451
00:22:25,226 --> 00:22:25,946
I'm strong.

452
00:22:26,146 --> 00:22:27,426
I can do it myself.

453
00:22:31,346 --> 00:22:36,280
(Fine Craftsmanship and Eco-Friendly
Materials Guard Environment)

454
00:22:36,280 --> 00:22:38,695
(Binhai First Road)

455
00:22:39,602 --> 00:22:43,250
(Huacai Printery)

456
00:22:45,305 --> 00:22:47,186
Everyone, move quickly and efficiently!

457
00:22:47,265 --> 00:22:47,765
Got it!

458
00:22:48,745 --> 00:22:51,025
Buddy, come and help.

459
00:22:51,585 --> 00:22:52,426
Sure, sir.

460
00:22:54,666 --> 00:22:55,545
Be careful!

461
00:22:55,785 --> 00:22:56,585
Handle it gently.

462
00:22:57,426 --> 00:22:59,466
Sun Xiaoyan reported to me today

463
00:23:00,025 --> 00:23:01,825
that her home had likely been burgled

464
00:23:02,265 --> 00:23:03,585
for several nights recently.

465
00:23:04,466 --> 00:23:05,426
This is intolerable!

466
00:23:06,946 --> 00:23:08,146
So, starting today,

467
00:23:08,265 --> 00:23:10,866
our main patrol area

468
00:23:11,065 --> 00:23:11,946
will be Ping'an Road.

469
00:23:12,305 --> 00:23:13,305
Everyone, be thorough.

470
00:23:13,825 --> 00:23:15,226
Don't overlook any corner.

471
00:23:15,666 --> 00:23:17,666
Also, be extremely careful.

472
00:23:17,906 --> 00:23:19,105
Do not alert the suspect.

473
00:23:19,545 --> 00:23:20,065
- Yes!
- Yes!

474
00:23:20,105 --> 00:23:20,706
Good.

475
00:23:21,065 --> 00:23:21,585
Move out!

476
00:23:21,825 --> 00:23:22,666
Turn left!

477
00:23:23,825 --> 00:23:24,706
March!

478
00:25:09,386 --> 00:25:10,986
Catch the thief!

479
00:25:12,825 --> 00:25:14,626
- Freeze!
- Freeze!

480
00:25:14,866 --> 00:25:16,146
- Freeze!
- Freeze!

481
00:25:16,386 --> 00:25:18,186
- Catch the bad guy!
- Catch him!

482
00:25:20,386 --> 00:25:20,886
Don't move!

483
00:25:21,065 --> 00:25:21,785
Don't move!

484
00:25:22,065 --> 00:25:22,785
Thanks, Mr. Tan.

485
00:25:22,825 --> 00:25:23,426
Catch him!

486
00:25:23,626 --> 00:25:24,585
- Catch him!
- Thank you.

487
00:25:24,585 --> 00:25:26,025
Let me go!

488
00:25:33,585 --> 00:25:35,025
What's wrong with you?

489
00:26:03,946 --> 00:26:04,866
Go to sleep!

490
00:26:05,505 --> 00:26:06,146
Go back!

491
00:26:07,785 --> 00:26:09,906
Mr. Xie, you made it.

492
00:26:10,986 --> 00:26:11,825
Your shirt...

493
00:26:12,545 --> 00:26:13,825
It's Ms. Gao's, isn't it?

494
00:26:21,426 --> 00:26:22,186
- I'm fine.
- Lin.

495
00:26:23,025 --> 00:26:24,345
I just strained my back.

496
00:26:29,545 --> 00:26:30,186
Lin,

497
00:26:31,105 --> 00:26:32,426
what were you thinking?

498
00:26:32,706 --> 00:26:34,585
I thought you were really over this.
But you...

499
00:26:36,186 --> 00:26:37,466
You haven't moved on at all.

500
00:26:39,626 --> 00:26:40,825
I can't believe you, Lin.

501
00:26:43,025 --> 00:26:44,866
You know perfectly well

502
00:26:45,666 --> 00:26:48,025
she's the spouse
of an active-duty soldier.

503
00:26:48,626 --> 00:26:51,105
You almost broke the criminal law.

504
00:26:51,545 --> 00:26:52,986
Luckily, nothing serious happened.

505
00:26:53,305 --> 00:26:55,545
Otherwise, it would be illegal!

506
00:26:56,186 --> 00:26:57,146
To be frank,

507
00:26:57,986 --> 00:26:58,986
the root of this problem

508
00:27:00,345 --> 00:27:01,745
lies with Li.

509
00:27:04,706 --> 00:27:05,386
Me?

510
00:27:08,345 --> 00:27:09,426
Let me lay it out for you.

511
00:27:10,505 --> 00:27:11,146
Look,

512
00:27:12,386 --> 00:27:13,825
Li failed

513
00:27:14,426 --> 00:27:16,866
to investigate the whole thing
thoroughly at the start,

514
00:27:17,626 --> 00:27:20,305
so it caused a misunderstanding
between Lin Dongfu

515
00:27:20,545 --> 00:27:21,666
and Sun Xiaoyan.

516
00:27:23,626 --> 00:27:24,585
As a result,

517
00:27:25,186 --> 00:27:26,706
Lin hasn't moved on yet.

518
00:27:27,825 --> 00:27:28,825
Also,

519
00:27:29,226 --> 00:27:30,466
an honest man like him

520
00:27:31,025 --> 00:27:33,226
nearly broke the law.

521
00:27:34,305 --> 00:27:35,146
What do you say?

522
00:27:36,226 --> 00:27:38,545
So you're saying

523
00:27:38,666 --> 00:27:41,025
I almost led him astray?

524
00:27:41,226 --> 00:27:43,065
Well, maybe not entirely...

525
00:27:43,065 --> 00:27:45,025
I really have moved on!

526
00:27:45,305 --> 00:27:46,265
It's just that

527
00:27:46,706 --> 00:27:47,946
I noticed

528
00:27:47,946 --> 00:27:49,745
Sun Xiaoyan's street cart had a problem.

529
00:27:50,065 --> 00:27:51,186
So, I wanted

530
00:27:51,426 --> 00:27:53,706
to figure out a way
to help her improve it.

531
00:27:54,345 --> 00:27:56,706
Then, it'll be easy for her to open up

532
00:27:56,866 --> 00:27:58,025
or close her stall.

533
00:27:58,386 --> 00:27:59,466
I meant nothing else.

534
00:28:00,025 --> 00:28:02,226
There is no need
for you to go every night.

535
00:28:02,345 --> 00:28:03,545
That's inappropriate.

536
00:28:03,626 --> 00:28:04,585
I was measuring it!

537
00:28:04,585 --> 00:28:06,226
How could I do it when she's using it?

538
00:28:06,305 --> 00:28:07,906
Why didn't you measure others' carts?

539
00:28:07,906 --> 00:28:09,186
You just haven't let go.

540
00:28:09,305 --> 00:28:10,706
Your heart is still full of her.

541
00:28:11,146 --> 00:28:13,666
Seriously, I'm touched. I feel for you!

542
00:28:13,706 --> 00:28:14,906
You're so devoted.

543
00:28:14,906 --> 00:28:16,825
- If I were her...
- I want a closure

544
00:28:16,825 --> 00:28:17,986
for myself, alright?

545
00:28:18,466 --> 00:28:20,186
Mr. Hailuo,

546
00:28:20,906 --> 00:28:22,146
has Mr. Lin gotten over it?

547
00:28:22,946 --> 00:28:23,866
Sure, he has.

548
00:28:24,386 --> 00:28:25,825
How could a man like him

549
00:28:25,825 --> 00:28:27,226
bury something like this inside?

550
00:28:28,505 --> 00:28:29,626
I'm sure he hasn't moved on.

551
00:28:29,745 --> 00:28:30,466
Be quiet!

552
00:28:32,146 --> 00:28:33,906
You're still young.
You don't understand.

553
00:28:34,505 --> 00:28:35,065
Lin,

554
00:28:35,265 --> 00:28:36,345
you really shouldn't think

555
00:28:36,345 --> 00:28:38,466
we're criticizing or lecturing you.

556
00:28:38,466 --> 00:28:39,065
- Okay!
- You...

557
00:28:39,065 --> 00:28:40,906
I promise! I swear!

558
00:28:41,906 --> 00:28:43,305
From now on,

559
00:28:44,226 --> 00:28:46,146
I'll have nothing
to do with Sun Xiaoyan!

560
00:28:46,305 --> 00:28:46,986
Okay.

561
00:28:47,146 --> 00:28:48,386
We all know that.

562
